data.description: Elegant home in desirable Carlton Ridge East! Open airy floor plan is great for people that love to entertain. Formal dining room w/ coffered ceilings, 5 true bedrooms, 2 living areas & 2 wood burning fireplaces. Spacious kitchen is a cooks' dream, stainless appliances, walk-in pantry, stellar island w/ lots of seating, cabinets galore and cozy breakfast area. When you walk through the double doors to your private master suite you will enjoy the luxurious garden tub and walk-in shower, 2 vanities & oversized walk-in closet.  There is a second master suite on the main level. All this and you still have paradise waiting outside.  Stone fireplace in your screened porch area overlooking 14x28 saltwater pool. Privacy fenced yard, 3 car garage and located in HOCO school district.
